### **Network Connectivity Issues**

#### Network Unreachable with Auto-Discovery
```bash
# Error: ENETUNREACH, Network is unreachable, no route to host
```

**Research Sources**:
- [Proxmox Networking Guide](mdc:https:/pve.proxmox.com/pve-docs/chapter-sysadmin.html#sysadmin_network_configuration)
- [Pulumi Network Discovery Patterns](mdc:https:/pulumi.com/docs/guides/testing)

**Auto-Recovery Implementation**:
```typescript
// Self-healing network discovery with fallback
export class AutoHealingNetworkDiscovery extends pulumi.ComponentResource {
  constructor(name: string, args: NetworkDiscoveryArgs) {
    super('infraflux:network:AutoHealingNetworkDiscovery', name, {});

    // Primary auto-discovery with fallback
    const networkConfig = this.discoverWithFallback(args);

    // Register self-healing monitor
    this.enableSelfHealing(networkConfig);
  }

  private async discoverWithFallback(args: NetworkDiscoveryArgs) {
    try {
      // Try auto-discovery first
      return await this.autoDiscoverNetwork(args);
    } catch (error) {
      logger.warn('Auto-discovery failed, using fallback', { error });
      return this.useFallbackConfiguration(args);
    }
  }
}
```

